description:
I invite you to cook with taro leaves if you havent yet. The pairing of taro leaves and coconut milk makes this dish unique and easily veganizable. In fact, my aunties would easily whip up this dish for me when I visit them. Dont be fooled by its simplicity and humble looks though. Theres a reason why its one of the most requested recipes on the blog. Laing packs a punch of flavor in every bite and leaves Laing fans hungry for more.

Kain na, lets eat!

TO BUY DRIED TARO LEAVES: http://amzn.to/26MxjZV

Here are simple steps to creating your own, authentic tofu. It may be hard to go back to store-bought tofu after learning how to make it from scratch. The taste is unbeatable. I hope you enjoy!
